{
  "stem": "10283.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I mean, we weren't-- I don't think we were hungry.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But we just got regular, you know, food that we-- they had food, but not on that scale that it was going there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had-- it was my first teenage time, really, that I was [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] more free than ever, especially going there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, I had-- I had a young man that befriended me and from-- and we were dancing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were playing shuffleboard and things like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yeah, I had friends.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had a very nice time going there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I don't think we had too many conversations.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because there was not much to say.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, we had to wait and see what's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Apart from the rumors, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we couldn't figure out what's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't think we talked too much about it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, very somber.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very somber.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The older people were very desperate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this came at the very end that we're going to be divided into these countries.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I think the same day as that came out, we were already in Antwerp when the same evening we-- we-- we got off the boat, and we came to Brussels.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, it just happened, so happened, that my mother's only brother was in Brussels and-- with his wife and son.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so it was-- in a way, it was nice for us that we were reunited with him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But and we were grateful that we landed in Belgium.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We didn't know that's going to be a war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we thought, well, we will have to start [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] procedure from there to immigrate somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We knew we cannot stay in Belgium.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, when we got off the boat, we had to sign that this is only temporary, and that we [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] promise that after times normalize, that we are going to leave Belgium again.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that came to haunt us later on when after the war, they wouldn't let us stay.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But we came to Brussels.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the American joined, more or less took care of us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We were a couple nights in a hotel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then they looked for housing for us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Well, [CHUCKLES] housing was-- Belgium, Brussels was a pretty old city, and especially at that time-- so they found terrible housing for us.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And coming from Germany, where we had, you know, not American comfort.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But we had all bathrooms, and bath tops, and kitchens, and everything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So finally, they found for us one room and a little kitchen for three people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the toilet-- no bathroom, I mean, no bathing facility.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the toilet was halfways between our floor and the floor above and was shared by all these people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were two or three little apartments like that on each floor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And every drop of water had to come from this bathroom and bought back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Dirty, you know, whatever, dish water or whatever had to be brought up the steps to this little bathroom.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was terrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my father-- my mother took it all in stride.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] she didn't flinch.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But my father was very depressed, and he couldn't-- he started to limp, and he smoked a lot.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he couldn't adjust too well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But my mother took it all in stride.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She-- of course, we got a little allowance, which was very, very little.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So she started to take in single men for-- for the noon meal.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she cooked, and they paid little, but enough so we could eat along with them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she always found a way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then she found, somehow, a place for me to be a nanny, so I get out of this environment.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because I-- I slept on a little cot in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my parents slept on the couch in the other room.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And-- and it was just not much.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she found a place for me with a Jewish family that had a little boy.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was supposed to be the nanny.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I got out of this, and I stayed with them, and more or less was a nanny [CHUCKLES] until-- I didn't see them really all that much, but-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] (WHISPERS) Can you stop it for me?",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How long were you with this family?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, till the war broke out in May, '40.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But something very strange happened during this time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- on my 16th birthday in Breslau, before we had left, I met a young man who was also 16, just been 16.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was introduced.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had-- my mother gave me a little birthday party, because we knew we had to leave.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
